profile:
Shop RHW is a Toronto-based studio with a focus on solid wood custom furniture hand crafted by Rundell Haynes-Wells. 
In addition to being a craftsman, he also offers custom design consultation and renderings.

Rundell combines years of experience problem solving, exploring, and innovating, and has been a maker of things all of his life. 
He’s a natural born collaborator and is generous with the information he shares with his clients in the hope that more knowledge and understanding of custom furniture will inspire sustained interest and appreciation.

Please give me a call - 647-453-0093

profile:
The Chesterfield Shop...Your Leather and Fabric Superstore & More!
Since 1948, this family owned and operated chain of Leather, Fabric and Home Theatre seating superstores, has been prouding serving generations of satisfied customers who keep coming back again and again for the great selection, quality, service and value..
You'll find an ocean of contemporary, stylish and colourful sofas, sofabeds (w/great mattresses for the most comfortable sleep), loveseats, chairs, sectionals, home theatre, recliners with power, ottomans with storage PLUS thousands of outstanding furnishing accessories like coffee and end tables, lamps, carpets, wall art & more.
With five convenient locations to serve you in the Toronto GTA and Newmarket. 
Huge Inventory, Special Orders, Leathers To Go Express™ Next Day Delivery on many stocked items, and even Delivery to Cottage Country!

Home Proud and Money Wise?  Come to The Chesterfield Shop.

profile:
Welcome to Alaev, 

With years of experience we bring professional furniture services to you. Our services include the moving and assembling of furniture. We specialize in Ikea, WayFair and Structube products, just to name a few. We will work with any brand! As well, we pride ourselves in our ability to quickly assemble, move or disassemble any type of furniture.


In addition, we offer Professional Painting services, as well as Drywall fixes and Patch work. We are here to help with your home renovation needs!


Let us transform any room with a fresh new coat of paint and newly assembled furniture, Alaev will professionally and honestly take care of of the tough stuff.
 

Follow us on Facebook and Instagram to keep up with our latest projects!
Call us to discuss what is possible.

profile:
Our company has been providing services to the business on furniture field including the products of furniture and interior design since 2001.

Palmiye Koçak, founded as a family company, is increasing its brand value and activities using 14-year experience, modern arguments against changing business circumstances with the same

name and same partnership today. Palmiye Koçak has one of the most comprehensive machine track in 5500 m2 closed area with architects (designers), professional staff of quality and leading.

Our company manufactures more than 5000 different kinds of secure “elegant and durable” products for institutional residences, houses, offices, hospitals, schools, pastry shops, cafes,

restaurants, hotels blending its developed infrastructure, 14-year-experience, professional crew and high quality products.

Palmiye Koçak exports the goods, which are manufactured in their own facilities, to more than 50 countries all around Europe, Asia, Africa and Middle East.

Countries from Asia: Russia, Georgia, Azerbaijan, Armenia, Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, Tajikistan. Turkmenistan, Japan,

Countries from Africa: Nigeria, Kenya, Libya, Algeria, Tunisia, Somalia, Sudan, Morocco, Mali,

Countries from Middle East: Saudi Arabia, Bahrain, United Arab Emirates, Iraq, Kuwait, Syria, UEA.

 

VISION

Our vision is to be one of the leading company in this field all around the world with our total quality management approach and strengthen our place in furniture sector via responding our partners’ with a higher performance.

MISSION

Our mission is to add new values to our human centered approach, develop our quality politics through “sustainability”, keep our relationships with our partners and dealers permanent on reliable bases by creating modern life environment with innovative approaches.

hanabanana art+design is your "one stop shop" for your projects!

We offer 3D architectural rendering services. We provide furniture and artworks.
Everything is customized for your projects!

As we love improvements, we commit to help design firms and businesses to work more effective, efficient and faster.

We are a team with various backgrounds, from architectural, interior design and digital artist.
Based in Toronto, hanabanana art+design helps to visualize our clients’ imaginations, from interior to exterior, from commercial to residential, from massive buildings to landscapes, from layouts to 3D renderings and animations.

We are art lovers, design nerds and marketing strategists.
We believe there is tremendous value in making architecture look sexier.

Our work will help you to showcase your designs as the best marketing tool for your clients.
